<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="business-n">business <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'bɪznəs/    美 /'bɪznəs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>商业；生意</strong></h4>
<p>the buying or selling of goods or services for money (commerce / trade)：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>go into business</strong>
经商</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>business hours</strong>
营业时间/办公时间</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We do not do much business with them.
我们和他们没有多少生意来往。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Business cards</strong> should be offered and received with two hands.
呈递和接收商务名片应用双手。</p><footer>2014 浙江</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>营业额；生意额：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Business is slow</strong> during the third quarter.
第三季度生意清淡。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>商务；公事</strong></h4>
<p>the work you do as your job：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We discussed the idea over a <strong>business lunch</strong>. 
我们在一次商务午餐时讨论了这一想法。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Father had left for London <strong>on business</strong> upon my arrival, so I didn’t see him. 
我回来时，父亲已去伦敦出差了，所以我没能见到他。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>职责；事务：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A teacher’s business is to teach. 
老师的职责是教学。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is <strong>none of your business</strong> what other people think about you.
别人怎么看你与你无关。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Mind your own business</strong>.
别管闲事。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>made it her business to</strong> take care of her younger sister after her mother died.
母亲去世后，她把照顾妹妹当作自己的责任。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.<strong>事情：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Leon regards keeping fit as <strong>a serious business</strong>.
莱昂认为保持健康很重要。</p></div>

<h4 id="6">6.★ <strong>公司；店铺；企业</strong></h4>
<p>(firm / company)：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The book is about how to design a website and <strong>start a business</strong>.
这是一本关于如何设计网站并创业的书。</p><footer>2012 山东</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>run a family business</strong>
经营家族企业</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="get-down-to-business">get down to business</h3>
<p>1.<strong>着手处理正事；开始认真办事：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>English and German cultures share similar values; however, Germans prefer to get down to business more quickly. 
英德文化有相似的价值观，然而，德国人更喜欢尽快办正事。</p></div>

<h3 id="mean-business">mean business</h3>
<p>1.<strong>［非正式用语］是认真的；是当真的</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="out-of-business">out of business</h3>
<p>1.<strong>停业；倒闭：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>One day, the boss told us that the company was out of business. 
一天，老板告诉我们公司倒闭了。</p></div></div>